= 1.4.1 (August 17, 2018) =
* Updated: API version

= 1.4.0 (May 23, 2017) =
* Added: Spinner module
* Updated: API version for Morrowind

= 1.3.0 (May 16, 2017) =
* Added: Support for custom timer notification sounds
* Added: Slash command to set custom unofficial notification sounds
* Added: Per-skill color options
* Added: Ability to lock the position of the UI
* Added: Option to display completed or remaining percentage instead of time remaining
* Improved: Handling of enabling account-wide settings for the first time
* Fixed: Bug which caused traits to be improperly identified in certain instances
* Fixed: Minor typo in "Carry Capacity"

= 1.2.3 (May 7, 2017) =
* Fixed: Typo in carry capacity riding trait

= 1.2.2 (May 6, 2017) =
* Fixed: Incorrectly getting trait indexes

= 1.2.1 (May 5, 2017) =
* Fixed: Riding timer abbreviation bug for stamina and capacity
* Fixed: Drain option completion background bug
* Fixed: Multi-character completed research bug

= 1.2.0 (May 3, 2017) =
* Improved: Settings layout
* Added: Option to display timers with a reverse fill (drain) effect
* Added: Option to abbreviate skill and trait names
* Added: Detail to stable timers

= 1.1.2 (May 1, 2017) =
* Improved: Announcement notification for stable timers
* Added: Keybinding to toggle timer display

= 1.1.1 (April 28, 2017) =
* Fixed: Chat notification display

= 1.1.0 (April 27, 2017) =
* Added: Notification support
* Added: /scholar timers command
* Fixed: Minor bug fixes

= 1.0.0 (April 26, 2017) =
* Added: Stable training timer
* Fixed: String bug

= 0.0.1 (April 23, 2017) =
* Initial release
